text: Aiglsbach is a town and municipality in Kelheim, Germany, and a member of the Mainburg administrative partnership, a voluntary resource-pooling agreement with three surrounding municipalities. ==Geography== Aiglsbach is between Regensburg and Munich, and between Ingolstadt and Landshut. The municipality has the following settlements: Aiglsbach, Berghausen, Gasseltshausen, Oberpindhart, Pöbenhausen, Radertshausen, Buch, Haselbuch, Gerblhäuser, Straßberg, Lindach and Moosham. ==References== Category:Kelheim (district)
